            Oil on Canvas
          </li>
          <li class="list-inline-item mr-3 text-muted">
            <span class="fas fa-ruler-combined text-muted mr-1"></span>
            65 x 51 x 2 cm
          </li>
        </ul>
        <!-- End Icon Blocks -->

        <p class="font-size-1">Salvador Dalí produced over 1,500 paintings in his career. He also produced illustrations for books, lithographs, designs for theater sets and costumes, a great number of drawings, dozens of sculptures, and various other projects, including an animated short film for Disney.</p>

        <p class="font-size-1">This is the painting in which he experimented with Cubism.</p>

        <!-- Financials -->
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center font-size-1">
          <p class="text-body">
            <span>
              <span class="fas fa-chart-line mr-2"></span>
